Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:04.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近哥哥總一個人偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概 是因為女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:12.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H1F293A&\bord5\blur5\fs70\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b1\fad(800,500)\pos(1116.876,559.752)}圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:09.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥 浴室空出來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,媽媽說讓你快去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:13.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,知 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:16.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼 密碼是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還在用入學考試的考號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:20.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真不小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川由紀 果然是這女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.02\bord2.5\fs35\c&H656363&\an1\move(386,292,350,180)}我是不是也差不多該\N去洗澡了呢（*‐*）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fs35\c&H656363&\an1\frz17.86\move(458,482,432,392)}啊！剛才肯定在\N想奇怪的東西吧（¬_¬）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fs35\c&H656363&\an1\frz16.52\move(780,500,758,412)}唔嗯唔嗯\N走好走好～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個誆騙哥哥的壞女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:28.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看我教訓你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 以後能別再和我說話了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,打擾我學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是小螢吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸…為什麼 我做了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說 是因為那件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:47.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,她做了什麼讓哥哥生氣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:51.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 挺像這女人做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:57.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但那件事不是古屋君你所渴求的嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,渴求…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:01:59.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是借了筆記之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:03.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白總之先嗆回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼無聊的事情你給我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:07.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好過分!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:08.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我明明也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:09.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,第一次的說‥!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,第一次? 什麼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥所渴求的同時還是這女人的第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:19.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 難道說是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,確實這事情是我渴求的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是約個會而已大家都在做的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,況且對我而言也是第一次約會的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然 沒懂呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:31.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那那場約會只是在玩弄我嗎??
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這段時間總是晚歸 果然是和這女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那和我睡覺也都是假的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,睡覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是一起睡過午覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,居然在約會的時候睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥也變奇怪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不過就睡了一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那肚子裡的孩子要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原來是這個意思啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但…但是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不做那種事的話就不會有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我哥哥這種人居然也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:19.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的是我的孩子嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你有證據嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:23.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我除了和古屋君以外的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒·再·睡·過·啊 {\c&H006A63ED}❤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,騙人的這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明 還只是高中生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 螢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你在我房裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,媽媽!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥他有孩子了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:54.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我和同班的女生開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:58.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,試著交往後 便有了想要珍惜她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 完全不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:06.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H686563&\bord5\blur5\fs70\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b1\fad(500,500)\pos(1006,584)}告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 和我在一起開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 嗯很開心喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說實話我對這種事情很不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是有哪裡不滿意的別客氣儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 就說一點可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:18.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 並不是很重要的事情就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:25.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得自己明白剛田君的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還是想聽你說出來呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,「我喜歡你」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:35.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 這種事情很麻煩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 這點小事也還好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼要特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:40.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也覺得自己像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但就是想聽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了上根 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:58.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,確實可能我至今 都沒有好好的說出自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,以後我多注意一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我不是在說以後耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我誤會什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:10.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可以的話現在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是呢 現在就應該展現誠意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 不我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 有什麼想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那…個 那…個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這次我們就一起去哪裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種叫法雖然很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算做是…第一次約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是的 我不是想去約會!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:35.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我現在就只想聽剛田君你說喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:36.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:40.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為剛田君 你還一次都沒為我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:46.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然約會也很開心 但我還是想聽這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為這樣的話不過是我讓你說這些的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:02.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 我好像說了些任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說起來 剛才說要約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 上根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:13.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 我喜歡你!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然現在無論說什麼都好像是你讓我說的一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:18.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的 打從心底喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我應該早點說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都怪我太遲鈍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 臉全紅了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近似乎總有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡在簡訊告白什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:43.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種人真的超爛的呢～（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:46.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是高瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,透過這種方式告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的感到很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但就是 喜歡高瀨你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為郵件發失敗了搞得很尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:03.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H00686D73\bord5\blur5\fs70\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b1\fad(500,0)\pos(1030.964,600.019)}建議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:02.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,神田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,由 小由紀 英語作業做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 有作業的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這絕對很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:15.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那之後的郵件也不知道她看沒看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要不再發一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 不能靠郵件得親口說才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:25.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是她都不聽我說 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不自覺的很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:35.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,很在意是說 什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我這個人嘴巴很笨拙可能說的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在的你跟以前的我一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個人怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我在哪見過這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 跟你沒關係 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是女人吧 一看就知道了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:55.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說了吧 你跟我很像的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也把女人弄哭得很慘過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我倒沒有弄哭得那麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但你還是弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,把最不想弄哭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找這個人商量的話說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你肯定以為我是戀愛達人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:17.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,戀愛? 咦? 在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到你我就會想起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個在雨中瑟瑟發抖的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你說怎麼樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:32.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對方都不跟我說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不知道 我是笨蛋所以完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:40.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,除了現在馬上跑過去緊緊抱住她之外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:41.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總覺得 被這麼一說就想這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你還在這磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:56.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 謝謝你給我這麼寶貴的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,建議? 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我只是說了自己想說的話而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這不過是一個被稱作戀愛達人的人說的傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好了 快去吧 她要回去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊對了 最後能不能告訴我前輩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前 前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近總有點恍神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上課時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是回過神來就發現自己在看奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且 胸口還有點難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H00686D73\bord5\blur5\fs70\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b1\fad(500,500)\pos(288.964,591.619)}都是發燒的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小千 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你最近很奇怪耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 可能是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:54.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我腦中總是閃過菅原的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:00.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種事還是第一次 真的是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:03.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,心跳得厲害了 肯定感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:12.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 感覺有點發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 社團活動的時候稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,醫務室的老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:23.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:24.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 不去足球部不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在說什麼啊我這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣下去完全聊不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,腦袋本來就有點恍惚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:41.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,得考慮一下話題才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:42.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你不是來量體溫什麼的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:52.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對啊 果然可能是發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我回社團那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:10.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不對 我是說我不知道體溫計在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.56,0:11:17.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這麼紅著臉跟我說 讓我有點心動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是吧 我的臉有這麼紅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 跟平時比起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 但是不應該是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我懂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野不懂談戀愛對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:39.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個是最新款好像五秒就能測出來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒發燒就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:43.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可是 如果沒有發燒的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果不是發燒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,正常體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是有點發燒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嗎! 快點回家比較好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我去社團那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:13.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是發燒的話 到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 滿身傷痕的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\3c&H007C7774\bord5\blur3\fs70\fn思源黑体 CN Light\b1\fad(500,0)\pos(655.364,473.219)}滿身傷痕的天使
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
