Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.27,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あの頃と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.86,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}熱を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:23.32,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}君といつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:28.62,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}同じ思い出ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.71,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.88,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:41.38,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.22,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.68,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:53.06,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:58.48,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:05.03,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:10.20,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:16.09,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:22.17,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:12.02,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}回首仰望過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:15.27,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}依然同那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.86,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}感受著你的熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:23.32,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}無論何時同你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:28.62,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}全都是同樣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.71,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}逐漸淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.88,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:41.38,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}害怕這逐漸的  忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.22,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.68,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想把這份風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:53.06,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}鎖進我的心裡  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:58.48,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想與你相見這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:05.03,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}卻很需要勇氣  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:10.20,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:16.09,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明天當我  睜開眼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:22.17,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你能在我身旁而已
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
